ERR-ANALYS (ERR-S) Statistical uncertainties were extracted from
           the MINUIT fitting procedure used through ROOT.
           (ERR-SYS) Systematic uncertainties were estimated by
           numerical comparison between multiple different fit
           attempts under different input conditions.
